{"tid":479812,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個發過最開心既夢","createTime":"2017-11-25T13:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T19:37:22.000Z","uid":157483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93c5fcfa9d818728260a2d732a6352844774b8a7","tid":479812,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"我有3個, 我盡量簡短講<br />\n<br />\n1. 比成班人追殺, 但係跑跑下原來有個女仔(外形似精靈, 金色長髮 尖耳仔 好靚好靚超級靚) 都比人追緊, 咁我地兩個拖住手一齊跑, 最後成功逃走然後一齊左, 跑既過程好sweet<br />\n<br />\n2. 清醒夢黎, 就係知自己發緊夢 可以控制夢境, 我即刻變左兩條女出黎做我女朋友然後兩個都扑哂(其中一個係akb某位公認好靚女既成員, 唔開名費事比人屌)<br />\n<br />\n3. 我地成班人比另一班好兇猛既人追殺, 我地被追殺果班人入面全部都係手無寸鐵既普通人, 但唯獨我係一個忍者(女忍者) 識忍術, 可以用隨心所欲用各種唔同既能力, 最後全部人都靠我保住"},{"pid":"f234dbbb8087df9690b989a007c3ed7d95eae717","tid":479812,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"發夢移民左去加拿大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba5ae0f42228ed85339168355781a4136f6b5fb","tid":479812,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"中意嘅女仔叫我奶佢鞋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1f5d4bb0113a04cca4b2b0de56e4645ed93bb8","tid":479812,"uid":72277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"夢到放低左ex<br />\n<br />\n先知自己真係放低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbcf7d293342907615b53333d26a003a44ddb2b","tid":479812,"uid":6285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T18:26:54.000Z","msg":"發夢同陳瀅影咗好多相<br />\n好close<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個夢好真實<br />\n醒咗打開電話 見到冇相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf8e808ddc7f5533937998e78b6c96fbc265e1c","tid":479812,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T18:40:35.000Z",